Package Service.Payment

Record Class PaymentConfirmationData

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
Service.Payment.PaymentConfirmationData
Record Components:
patronName - name of the user who made the payment
amountPaid - amount that was paid
paymentDate - date of the payment
receiptId - unique receipt identifier
paymentMethod - method used for the payment
transactionId - transaction reference ID
processedBy - name of the staff or system that processed the payment
previousBalance - user's balance before payment
remainingBalance - user's balance after payment
currency - currency of the transaction
public record PaymentConfirmationData(String patronName, String amountPaid, String paymentDate, String receiptId, String paymentMethod, String transactionId, String processedBy, String previousBalance, String remainingBalance, String currency) extends Record
Holds information about a user's payment confirmation details.
